abstract: The United States has postponed a meeting of leaders of southeast Asian nations that was set for Las Vegas in mid-March due to the spread of the coronavirus, a senior Trump administration official and the Philippine ambassador said.
snippet: The United States has postponed a meeting of leaders of southeast Asian nations that was set for Las Vegas in mid-March due to the spread of the coronavirus, a senior Trump administration official and the Philippine ambassador said.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — The United States has postponed a meeting of leaders of southeast Asian nations that was set for Las Vegas in mid-March due to the spread of the coronavirus, a senior Trump administration official and the Philippine ambassador said.
headline_main: US Postpones Southeast Asian Leaders' Meeting Due to Virus
headline_print_headline: US Postpones Southeast Asian Leaders' Meeting Due to Virus

abstract: The accusations came as other elements of the federal government moved to head off a broader wave of infections like those in China.
snippet: The accusations came as other elements of the federal government moved to head off a broader wave of infections like those in China.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — President Trump and members of his administration mobilized on Friday to confront the threat of the coronavirus — not just the outbreak, but the news media and the Democrats they accused of exaggerating its danger.

abstract: The latest confirmed case of coronavirus in the United States, diagnosed in a California woman, is of "unknown origin" and was found in a patient who had not traveled overseas or had contact with any known travelers, local health officials said on Friday.
snippet: The latest confirmed case of coronavirus in the United States, diagnosed in a California woman, is of "unknown origin" and was found in a patient who had not traveled overseas or had contact with any known travelers, local health officials said on...
lead_paragraph: LOS ANGELES — The latest confirmed case of coronavirus in the United States, diagnosed in a California woman, is of "unknown origin" and was found in a patient who had not traveled overseas or had contact with any known travelers, local health officials said on Friday.
headline_main: New Coronavirus Case in California Is of Unknown Origin
headline_print_headline: New Coronavirus Case in California Is of Unknown Origin

abstract: In an epidemic, suppression of bad news costs lives and eventually angers the public. The White House is in danger of repeating the error.
snippet: In an epidemic, suppression of bad news costs lives and eventually angers the public. The White House is in danger of repeating the error.
lead_paragraph: Many times in many countries, political leaders have tried to censor health officials and play down the risks of infection just as epidemics approached.

abstract: Michael R. Bloomberg, trying to convey the competence and cool-headedness he says are missing in the White House, will air a new three-minute commercial nationally on Sunday.
snippet: Michael R. Bloomberg, trying to convey the competence and cool-headedness he says are missing in the White House, will air a new three-minute commercial nationally on Sunday.
lead_paragraph: CLARKSVILLE, Tenn. — Hobbled by lackluster debate performances and with time running short, Michael R. Bloomberg is trying to refocus his presidential campaign on his experience dealing with disasters as the mayor of New York, hoping to draw a stark contrast with President Trump’s handling of the coronavirus and the managerial records of some of his Democratic opponents.

abstract: The stock market had its worst week since 2008, signaling that one of the longest expansions in history could be ending. Policymakers said they were ready to act.
snippet: The stock market had its worst week since 2008, signaling that one of the longest expansions in history could be ending. Policymakers said they were ready to act.
lead_paragraph: Investors, fearing that the spread of the coronavirus is tipping the global economy into a recession, handed the stock market its largest weekly loss since the 2008 financial crisis on Friday amid worries that one of the longest economic expansions in history may be coming to an end.

abstract: At the annual gathering of conservatives, one Republican was conspicuously absent among the Trump supporters — Mitt Romney. The conference organizer said he had been disinvited.
snippet: At the annual gathering of conservatives, one Republican was conspicuously absent among the Trump supporters — Mitt Romney. The conference organizer said he had been disinvited.
lead_paragraph: OXON HILL, Md. — Donald J. Trump was still a New York businessman when he was booed at the Conservative Political Action Conference in 2015 after he proposed fighting ISIS with troops on the ground in the Middle East.

abstract: U.S. President Donald Trump is willing to hold a summit with the leaders of Russia, China, Britain and France - the five permanent members of the U.N. Security Council - to discuss arms control, a senior administration official said on Friday.
snippet: U.S. President Donald Trump is willing to hold a summit with the leaders of Russia, China, Britain and France - the five permanent members of the U.N. Security Council - to discuss arms control, a senior administration official said on Friday.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — U.S. President Donald Trump is willing to hold a summit with the leaders of Russia, China, Britain and France - the five permanent members of the U.N. Security Council - to discuss arms control, a senior administration official said on Friday.
headline_main: Trump Willing to Meet Leaders of Russia, China, Britain, France on Arms Control
headline_print_headline: Trump Willing to Meet Leaders of Russia, China, Britain, France on Arms Control

abstract: The United States has decided to postpone a meeting with leaders of Southeast Asian countries it had planned to host on March 14 due to worries about the coronavirus outbreak, two U.S. officials familiar with the matter said on Friday.
snippet: The United States has decided to postpone a meeting with leaders of Southeast Asian countries it had planned to host on March 14 due to worries about the coronavirus outbreak, two U.S. officials familiar with the matter said on Friday.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — The United States has decided to postpone a meeting with leaders of Southeast Asian countries it had planned to host on March 14 due to worries about the coronavirus outbreak, two U.S. officials familiar with the matter said on Friday.
headline_main: U.S. Postpones Summit With ASEAN Leaders Amid Coronavirus Fears: Sources
headline_print_headline: U.S. Postpones Summit With ASEAN Leaders Amid Coronavirus Fears: Sources

abstract: President Donald Trump said on Friday he again was tapping Republican Representative John Ratcliffe to be the nation's top spy, a loyalist whose first nomination he dropped last year amid questions about a lack of experience and possible resume embellishment.
